text: Frédéric Lemoine (born 13 March 1970) is a French gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pantin
